title: Genevieve Aer and Sofiya Alexandra
itunes:title: Genevieve Aer and Sofiya Alexandra
description:
Whitney's Ukrainian Russian friend Genevieve Aer (Liberty Horse Trainer) and Comedian Sofiya Alexandra (writer and comedian) were both born in Ukraine and are here to answer all our stupid questions about the war with Russia and growing up there.  For reliable news and different ways to help go to: https://help-ukraine.crd.co/ // www.care.org // www.comebackalive.in.ua 

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
